  <div class="page-body">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="prose">

        <div class="verdict">✓ Updated April 2026</div>

        <p>Buildertrend and Houzz Pro are both marketed to remodeling contractors, but they take fundamentally different approaches. Buildertrend is a construction project management platform that added client-facing features. Houzz Pro is a design community platform that added business management tools. Which philosophy fits your business determines which one you should use.</p>

